{"tid":1480094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非好應該去了解自己做緊乜","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:45.000Z","uid":4660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18c07be5562ed80ff368ffab84960454f911108c","tid":1480094,"uid":4660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"點解咁多行動派會話遊行無用？<br />\n<br />\n因為遊行只係止於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治表態</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地只係話俾人知你不滿，要求佢做野...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果民主國家都仲好，至少會聽你地講，<br />\n<br />\n但我地面對緊既係一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極權政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你地叫得幾大聲佢地都唔會理你，<br />\n<br />\n所以遊行左廿年都無成果就係咁解...<br />\n<br />\n係時候進步喇，要做和理非<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你可以罷工罷學、按章工作、唔交稅去癱瘓政府運作<br />\n<br />\n咁樣先真真正正咁俾到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壓力</span></span>依個政府，要佢回應我地訴求"},{"pid":"2c82d0c0cfe080ea1f554cc8c95597b1fd42748c","tid":1480094,"uid":20283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 818要人呀 幫手推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}